neffect of an existing bulk read/write optimization for CouchDB during state\nvalidation & commit phase (2.5x improvement). By combining all three\noptimizations1, we improved the overall throughput by 16x (i.e., from 140 tps\nto 2250 tps).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 May 2018 12:30:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-30"}
